                References in Text
              </h3>
              <p>
                This chapter, referred to in subsec. (b), was in the original "this Act", meaning , known as the
                Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974. Titles I, III, and IV of such Act are classified
                principally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note
                set out under and Tables.
              </p>
              <p>
                The Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act of 1996, referred to in subsec. (b), is , , .
                For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title of 1996 Amendment note set out
                under , The Public Health and Welfare, and Tables.
              </p>
