              </p>
              <p>
                Subsec. (a). , struck out "(1)" after subsec. designation and struck out par. (2) which read as follows:
                "A plan description (containing the information required by subsection (b)) of any employee benefit plan
                shall be prepared on forms prescribed by the Secretary, and shall be filed with the Secretary as
                required by . Any material modification in the terms of the plan and any change in the information
                described in subsection (b) shall be filed in accordance with ."
